high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the end of the table, then turn left again and go past the table, then turn right going around to the other side of the table.
Pick up the credit card in front of the cardboard box on the right side of the coffee table.
Move over to your left so that you are in front of the cardboard box on the left side of the coffee table.
Place the credit card in the cardboard box on the left side of the coffee table.
Pick up the box with the credit card inside.
Turn around so that you are facing the red couch.
Place the box with the credit card inside on the right side of the remote, on the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put a box containing a credit card on the couch.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk around to the other side of the coffee table.
Pick up the credit card off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk over to the couch, then turn right and walk around to the other side of the coffee table.
Put the credit card in the rightmost cardboard box on the coffee table.
Pick up the cardboard box with the credit card in it off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left to face the red couch.
Put the cardboard box with the credit card in it on the seat of the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a credit card in it on the couch.

high_descs: Move around to the other side of the coffee table, turn to face the card on the table.
Pick up the card on the table.
Bring the card back around to the other side of the table, face the box on the right side of the table.
Put the card in the right box on the table.
Pick up the box with card on the table.
Turn around, bring the box to the red couch.
Put the box with card on the red couch.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a credit card in it on the red couch.
